Remodeled Master Bath with Tiled Frameless Shower, Free Standing Tub, & BarnDoor! Half Bathroom w'Marble Counter & Hand Built Sink Stand. Garage w'Built-ins, Workbench, Space for Freezer or Fridge & Back up Battery to open Door During Power Outage. Other Features Include: Fresh Paint , New Carpet, Elongated Toilets & Neighborhood Includes Pool, Park, Playground, Pond & Greenbelt!
